Package by.horant.fintask.service.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientServiceImpl
    This class is an implementation of the ClientService interface and thus provides client interaction with the application by implementing such methods as authorization and registration.
    DataServiceImpl
    This class is an implementation of the DataService interface and thus provides interaction with several types of entity classes, implementing such methods as obtaining users, receiving orders, receiving medicines and obtaining the requested prescriptions.
    OrderServiceImpl
    This class is an implementation of the OrderService interface and thus provides interaction with the order.
    PrescriptionServiceImpl
    This class is an implementation of the PrescriptionService interface and thus provides interaction with the recipe.
    UpdateServiceImpl
    This class is an implementation of the UpdateService interface and thus provides updating user data.
